reviewText: when I watched this video I learned a lot about Brooks and Dunn and how they came up with there music

I watached on my computer; so the clarity quality may be better on HD TV.  Loved the information; learned alot that I didn't know. Would like to see one done on Ronnie Dunn by himself.  He has a unique voice & I'm glad to have hisi music in my life.
Used to hate country music....but the change in Rock & Pop & Rapp have changed the style of Country Music.  Ronnie Dunn's CD "RONNIE DUNN" is excellent.

Have purchased many dvd's from this person in the past and will continue to do so. He is very prompt in delivering the merchandise to us. My husband and I are very much into good bios of some of our famous people to see how they came about. I would recommend this bio to anyone who likes Brooks and Dunn.
